    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require all buses to have air conditioning",
        "additional_details": "We are getting hotter summers and we think having no air conditioning causes a risk to drivers who may have to sit in 30\u00b0c+ all day long. We are concerned that drivers could pass out due to the heat and cause catastrophic damage to passengers, other road user and themselves.",
        "background": "We want the government to make it compulsory for all buses to have air conditioning.",
